      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，\"Go to work\"部分已添加：泡茶5分、上楼3分、工作1分（你和猫）。现在处理\"Go home\"部分？",
      "elements_involved": [
