      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，回家部分简单些：先\"Go downstairs\"下楼，5分；然后\"Sit down\"坐下休息，3分。都是我自己。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Go downstairs",
